In saucepan, crumble tube of ready-to-heat grits, and heat over medium heat with 1/2 cup coconut milk until hot and creamy, about 5 minutes. Add corn kernels. Continue cooking for another 5 minutes. Add olive oil, salt, and chives and combine well before portioning into 4 bowls. Garnish with sundried tomatoes, avocado slices, and the reserved chive. Serve with your favorite hot sauce.